'Dengan karunia Tuhan Krishna'

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:17.760
'Karn dan Uruvi bersatu'

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:19.440
'dalam tubuh, pikiran dan jiwa.'

00:10:19.640 --> 00:10:22.920
'Uruvi mendapatkan cinta Radha'

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:26.640 line:20%
